    {
      "id": "PopularPost8167",
      "post_content": "Good sideboard tech against a lot of tricks in this block, including [Mogg Fanatic](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mogg Fanatic), [Auratog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Auratog), [Rootwalla](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rootwalla) and even enchantments like [Goblin Bombardment](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Bombardment). Wrecks [Morphling](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Morphling), etc... Really in the end this card wrecks a surprisingly high number of tactics and combat tricks. Great for decks with big creatures that just don't need those tricks. Ruins flowstone too.",
      "posted_by": "kitsunewarlock",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost8167\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Good sideboard tech against a lot of tricks in this block, including <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mogg Fanatic\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mogg Fanatic\">Mogg Fanatic</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Auratog\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Auratog\">Auratog</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rootwalla\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rootwalla\">Rootwalla</a> and even enchantments like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Bombardment\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Bombardment\">Goblin Bombardment</a>.  Wrecks <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Morphling\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Morphling\">Morphling</a>, etc...  Really in the end this card wrecks a surprisingly high number of tactics and combat tricks.  Great for decks with big creatures that just don't need those tricks.  Ruins flowstone too.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '8167'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy486\">kitsunewarlock</span>\r\n                                (6/2/2009 4:05:51 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">