      "id": "PopularPost149301",
      "post_content": "It has some niche uses. The most important effect of this card I can think of is its nullification of protection lands like [Maze of Ith](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Maze of Ith), [Mystifying Maze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mystifying Maze) and [Kor Haven](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kor Haven), since they can target only attacking creatures.",
